import React, { useState } from "react";
import {
  Box,
  Grid,
  Text,
  Flex,
  Accordion,
  Center,
  Avatar,
  Badge,
  Checkbox,
  Button,
  ColorPicker,
  Input,
  Stack,
  Image,
  Card,
  Slider,
  ActionIcon,
} from "@mantine/core";

import {
  IconPlus,
  IconX,
  IconColumns1,
  IconBold,
  IconUnderline,
  IconItalic,
  IconLetterN,
} from "@tabler/icons-react";
import { Dropzone, IMAGE_MIME_TYPE } from "@mantine/dropzone";

const CustomizeCategoryList3 = () => {
  {
    /* Dropzone */
  }

  const [files, setFiles] = useState([]);

  const previews = files.map((file, index) => {
    const imageUrl = URL.createObjectURL(file);
    return (
      <Image
        key={index}
        src={imageUrl}
        onLoad={() => URL.revokeObjectURL(imageUrl)}
      />
    );
  });
  return (
    <Accordion m="xs" variant="contained">
      {/* All Product */}
      <Accordion.Item value="all-product">
        <Accordion.Control bg="gray.2" direction="row">
          <Flex justify="flex-start" align="center" direction="row" gap="md">
            <Checkbox defaultChecked />
            <Text>All Product</Text>
          </Flex>
        </Accordion.Control>
        <Accordion.Panel>
          <Flex direction="column">
            <Text mt="xs">Background Color</Text>
            <ColorPicker mt="xs" w="auto" size="lg" format="rgba" />
          </Flex>
          <Flex direction="column">
            <Text mt="xs">Level</Text>
            <Input placeholder="Input component" />
          </Flex>
        </Accordion.Panel>
      </Accordion.Item>
      {/* Electronics */}
      <Accordion.Item value="electronics2">
        <Accordion.Control bg="gray.2" direction="row">
          <Flex justify="flex-start" align="center" direction="row" gap="md">
            <Checkbox defaultChecked />
            <Text>Electronics</Text>
          </Flex>
        </Accordion.Control>
        <Accordion.Panel>
          <Flex direction="column">
            <Text mt="xs">Background Color</Text>
            <ColorPicker mt="xs" w="auto" size="lg" format="rgba" />
          </Flex>
          <Flex direction="column">
            <Text mt="xs">Level</Text>
            <Input placeholder="Input component" />
          </Flex>
        </Accordion.Panel>
      </Accordion.Item>
      {/* Clothing */}
      <Accordion.Item value="clothing2">
        <Accordion.Control bg="gray.2" direction="row">
          <Flex justify="flex-start" align="center" direction="row" gap="md">
            <Checkbox defaultChecked />
            <Text>Clothing</Text>
          </Flex>
        </Accordion.Control>
        <Accordion.Panel>
          <Flex direction="column">
            <Text mt="xs">Background Color</Text>
            <ColorPicker mt="xs" w="auto" size="lg" format="rgba" />
          </Flex>
          <Flex direction="column">
            <Text mt="xs">Level</Text>
            <Input placeholder="Input component" />
          </Flex>
        </Accordion.Panel>
      </Accordion.Item>
    </Accordion>
  );
};

export default CustomizeCategoryList3;
